   <text type="letter">
      <body>
         
            <opener>
               <dateline rend="right">
                  <name type="place">ATTORNEY GENERAL'S OFFICE, <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>,</name>
                  <date when="1866-11-03">Nov. 3, <hi rend="italic">1866.</hi>
                  </date>
               </dateline>
               <salute>Dear Hinton,</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>The bearer, my friend, Mr. Shambaugh,<ptr target="khs.00001_n2"/> was showing me a letter he has received, (he is on a Committee of Sold. &amp; Sail. Union League)&#8212;I think it ought to be published in full. You make a brief introduction to it &amp; let it go in a Sunday Chronicle.<ptr target="khs.00001_n3"/> Let him have a proof when it is set up, to bring to me.</p>
            <p>Yours &amp;c</p>
            <closer rend="right">
               <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
         
      </body>
   </text>
